  ('ai-agents','superagi','SuperAGI','Open-source autonomous AI agent platform.','SuperAGI lets you spawn, manage, and deploy autonomous agents with tool integrations, a GUI, and performance telemetry—fully self-hostable.','https://superagi.com',null,true,'Unlimited (self-host)','Free (open-source)',false,'{"superagi","open-source","platform"}','SuperAGI — Free Open-Source Autonomous Agent Platform','SuperAGI: free open-source platform for building autonomous AI agents.'),
